  "description": "Design System Builder \\u2014 Figma MCP Skill workflow skill. Use this skill when the user needs Build or update a professional-grade design system in Figma from a codebase. Use when the user wants to create variables/tokens, build component libraries, set up theming (light/dark modes), document foundations, or reconcile gaps between code and Figma. This skill teaches WHAT to build and in WHAT ORDER \\u2014 it complements the figma-use skill which teaches HOW to call the Plugin API. Both skills should be loaded together and the operator should rely on the packaged workflow, support pack, troubleshooting notes, and provenance links before merging or handing off.",
